caption:
Quick eyeliner tip from @janineintansari😍❤️
-
“How I currently draw my eyeliner,
It’s a half-eyeliner style, I only draw from the middle of the eye to the outer, making a wing-eyeliner look, but I don’t draw on the inner corner, leaving it empty 🧐
.
I think this way, your eyelid will show even more, also for you who has monolid, this is the perfect way to still have a wing-eyeliner look without having to draw your eyeliner so thick? Just draw on the outside, right 😁👍🏼
.
I hope you enjoy this tutorial,
Tag me if you recreate this half-eyeliner look so I can repost it on my stories, I really LOVE the new story tag notification feature that Instagram just added in, SUPER useful🤩
Now I will not miss a single tag from you all 🤩💖👍🏼✨”
